# OpenCode Go API key — copy this to opencode-go.env and fill in your key.
# Three options (pick one):

# Option 1: Plain key (recommended for most users)
# OPENCODE_GO_API_KEY=sk-...

# Option 2: Proton Pass vault reference (requires pass-cli)
# OPENCODE_GO_API_KEY=pass://your-vault/Your%20Item/OPENCODE_GO_API_KEY

# Option 3: Leave this file empty and export OPENCODE_GO_API_KEY in your shell
# before starting the proxy.
